title: Translations of the Meanings of the Quran in 31 Languages-Part1
description:
Translations of the Meanings of the Qur'an in 31 Languages - Part 1:

This is a special 3-parts upload where we have Translations of the Holy Qur'an in 31 languages. These are all official translations authorized by King-Fahd Complex for the Printing of the Holy Qur'an, in Madinah Munawwarah, Saudi Arabia.

In Part 1, we have the following:

-  The_Noble_Qur'an_in_Albanian

-  The_Noble_Qur'an_in_Brahui

- The_Noble_Qur'an_in_Burmese_Volume_1

-  The_Noble_Qur'an_in_Burmese_Volume_2

-  The_Noble_Qur'an_in_Chichewa

-  The_Noble_Qur'an_in_Chinese

-  The_Noble_Qur'an_in_English

-  The_Noble_Qur'an_in_Filipino

-  The_Noble_Qur'an_in_French

-  The_Noble_Qur'an_in_German

-  The_Noble_Qur'an_in_Greek
